{"tid":452298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[留下奶粉]環時促當局表態：澳洲對中國沒那麼重要","createTime":"2017-10-30T05:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T15:24:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44a2f8910c8b407a237b7c0d0633f0ed3eda41a8","tid":452298,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E8%AB%96%E4%BF%83%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%92%E9%82%A3%E9%BA%BC%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81-%E8%8B%A5%E6%87%82%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%BE%E8%91%97%E5%B0%BE%E5%B7%B4%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E8%99%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2586-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25AB%2596%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2582%25A3%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%2587%2582%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E8%2591%2597%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%2599%2595%2F&d=smCtCamarhrpjCAdrbEdakjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=7ac53326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2586-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25AB%2596%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2582%25A3%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%2587%2582%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E8%2591%2597%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%2599%2595%2F&h=86b04c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E8%AB%96%E4%BF%83%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%92%E9%82%A3%E9%BA%BC%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81-%E8%8B%A5%E6%87%82%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%BE%E8%91%97%E5%B0%BE%E5%B7%B4%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E8%99%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》今日發表社論，回應上周有中國留學生在澳洲被打。該文指澳洲的學校「沒那麼不可取代」，又指整個澳洲「對中國也沒那麼重要」，澳洲如果「懂得在亞洲夾著尾、而不是翹著尾巴做人，對它應該是更有好處的。」<br />\n<br />\n該社論以〈澳有義務認真保護中國學生安全〉為題，批評澳洲有太多「辱華、仇華」的新聞，澳洲總理、外長對中國說重話，主流媒體宣揚「中國威脅論」等。文章指，「要多麼理性的中國人」，才會相信「那個國家」（澳洲）對中國友好。<br />\n<br />\n社論亦指，澳洲的學校「沒那麼不可取代」，更指「整個澳大利亞對中國也沒那麼重要」，「它如果懂得在亞洲夾著尾巴、而不是翹著尾巴做人，對它應該是更有好處的。」<br />\n<br />\n社論最後表示，澳洲有「壞孩子」不足為奇，孩子做了錯事，家長的態度是最緊要的。現在到了澳洲社會的「家長」就這段時間各種「壞孩子」的劣行做一個表態的時候了。「希望看到『澳家的家長』是講德講理的，對自己孩子不護短的」。<br />\n<br />\n上周一（23日），有兩名在澳洲首都坎培拉讀高中的中國留學生，在一個巴士站候車時，被4名當地少年上前，問他們是否有煙。兩人回應沒有後，即被對方以歧視言語侮辱，隨後亦有逾20人從剛到站的巴士衝下來加入，將兩名中國留學生圍毆。一個女學生在路過勸止時亦被打。<br />\n<br />\n坎培拉警方已拘捕兩名涉案少年，並將會在兒童法庭提訊。當地警方及教育部門亦就事件，與華人社區領袖、學生及家長等會面，商討學生人身安全等議題。"},{"pid":"e2c2e687e0a562e4df72da636b725db74a693994","tid":452298,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:13:57.000Z","msg":"咁好啦，叫班駐澳支那五毛躝回支那"},{"pid":"4cb2b018482482e3124f062815cc8a90170089ff","tid":452298,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:24:56.000Z","msg":"Redbaron85163冒認我<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/452808/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/452808/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/223419_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F223419_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=39741c00&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}